{"tid":26140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先食潭仔 柒到喊","createTime":"2016-12-06T14:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T09:39:48.000Z","uid":40637,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3230fa2e8c923932891f557894a0bc3d63e88878","tid":26140,"uid":40637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:16:23.000Z","msg":"頭先食潭仔 仲有15分鐘就關鋪<br />\n我一條友on99咁叫左3隻土匪雞翼，<br />\n點知唔夠幾分鐘有條仔入左黎 又叫，但個呀姐話「 矛哂啦 」結果佢只係叫左碗麵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔知點解有種傻9唸法 之後 我行左過去同佢講<br />\n「 我有兩隻食唔哂，請你食！」<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n「 下，你個啲土匪雞翼嚟，我食香草架喳！」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個下柒到無地自容 想翻入呀媽個西窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2564ddb74d62194321251d74f5960aac07755aa9","tid":26140,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:17:20.000Z","msg":"87分，不能再高了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f452caf7723acdc295ac255092e9f7ee602bcd","tid":26140,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"🤔"},{"pid":"dbdd6fd72a0eb452b6b8fde6a2b7891da1b048a3","tid":26140,"uid":3226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>87分，不能再高了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cb4fc0e6e5f11723bef07ce6a6628bd0ed4274","tid":26140,"uid":51090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>87分，不能再高了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想問好耐，依句係咪支那用語？"},{"pid":"736a9a20c245dbb5d121ffeb217afa859623bf90","tid":26140,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:19:37